text:
A general view, north from 2 Horatio Street, at Greenwich Ave.

March 16, 1933.

P. L. Sperr.
title: General view - [Manhattan - Horatio Street (North) - Greenwich Avenue.]

text:
(1) A general view, northeast, from 2 Horatio Street, at Greenwich Ave., showing in the background from left to right, the Empire State Building, (34th St., and Fifth Ave), the Chrysler Building, (42nd St., and Lexington Ave) and the Metropolitan Life Insurance Building, (Madison Ave., at 23rd St).

March 16, 1933.

P. L. Sperr.

(2) The same, without the Metropolitan Life and the Chrysler buildings.

March 16, 1933.

P. L. Sperr.
